data.description: Welcome to 221 Northfield Way in the sought after North Brook Community.  This GORGEOUS brick front colonial is ready for you to move right in!  As you walk into this home, you are greeted with a stunning 2 story foyer that is wide open with hardwood floors, a double staircase, and perfect finishings.  To the immediate right you have the main level home office.  (This room could also be used as a playroom, separate tv room, or whatever you need it to be.)  Coming back into the foyer you have the large living room to the left and that is all open to the HUGE dining room.  Plenty of space for gatherings and holidays!   As you walk down the hallway from the foyer, you have a half bathroom,  and then it opens up to the open floor plan with the GORGEOUS kitchen and OVERSIZED family room with all new flooring.  The kitchen is STUNNING.  Large island with cooktop, ample cabinet and counter space, double wall ovens, and eat in table space.  The OVERSIZED family room boasts a gas fireplace surrounded by stone, and a plethora of natural sun light beaming in.  Off of the kitchen you will find the relaxing 3 seasons room.  Come enjoy the warm days and nights out here and escape for a while.  Moving upstairs you will find a large hallway, 4 HUGE bedrooms, laundry room, and 2 full bathrooms.  Each secondary bedroom offers ample closet space.  The hallway bathroom boasts a double vanity, tile floors and a tile shower.  The owner's suite is PERFECTION.  Large, open, with vaulted ceilings, and boasting a gas fireplace to give that it that sense of calmness.  Off of the owner's suite is a whole other space that can be used in so many ways: sitting room, home gym, home office, closet, craft room, or possible 5th bedroom.  The possibilities are endless with this room!  The walk in closet is what you have been waiting for!!! Room for EVERYTHING!!  Moving into the LARGE owner's suite bathroom, you will find, tile floors, his and her vanities, soaking tub and tile shower.  Moving back downstairs to the main level, you will find a conditioned and finished 4 ft crawlspace that is the ENTIRE length of the house.  This is PERFECT for STORAGE.  You can actually USE your 2 car garage to park your cars into because it offers so much storage!!!   Out back of the home will find a nice sized deck and yard.  Brand NEW roof just installed 2 weeks ago!!!  The community offers a playground, soccer field, pavilion, walking path, ponds, and woods to explore!  This home is ready for YOU to make it your own.  Don't let this one slip by!!!
